name: Pearl Jam
profile: Alternative Rock (Modern Rock) band from Seattle, Washington (USA), formed from the ashes of Jeff and Stone's previous band [a=Mother Love Bone] and the [a=Temple of the Dog] tribute project. Inducted to the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame in 2017.
